OL,3,CGuernsey Major hidden account of D-Day
OL,4,Cunveiled for the first time
OL,6,FMore than 20 years after a man died,
OL,7,Fhis family have discovered the
OL,8,Fsignificant role he played in D-Day.
OL,10,FIn the vaults of a regimental museum,
OL,11,Fcurators have uncovered an archive
OL,12,Ffrom the Normandy Landings which
OL,13,Fcontained the stories from D-Day
OL,14,Fwritten by those there.
OL,16,FOne of those was Major Terry Brock
OL,17,Ffrom La Corbiere in the Forest, a
OL,18,Fyoung officer with the Warwickshire
OL,19,Fregiment.
