OL,6,FMajor Brock was educated at Rugby
OL,7,Fschool and attached to the
OL,8,FWarwickshires.
OL,10,FHe had always told his family he
OL,11,Flanded on the Normandy beaches three
OL,12,Fdays after D-Day, but the newly
OL,13,Fdiscovered archives reveal he was at
OL,14,Fthe heart of the action.
