OL,6,FHis grandson, Oliver Brock says his
OL,7,Fgrandfather lied for years, he says:
OL,8,F"What my father tells me is that his
OL,9,Ffather (Major Terry Brock) told him,
OL,10,Fand his siblings that he arrived on
OL,11,Fthe D-Day beaches three days after D-
OL,12,FDay occurred, he kind of just rolled
OL,13,Fin."
