OL,6,FThe family themselves discovered more
OL,7,Fabout his role in D-Day when they
OL,8,Ffound an old leather briefcase locked
OL,9,Faway in a secret drawer, In it were
OL,10,Fmore of Major Brock's documents from
OL,11,Fthe war, including medals and letters
OL,12,Fwhich commended his courageous
OL,13,Fdevotion to duty.
OL,15,FHe had also hidden an award of a
OL,16,FBronze Lion from Queen Wilhelmina of
OL,17,Fthe Netherlands for distinguishing
OL,18,Fhimself during the operations for the
OL,19,Fliberation of the Netherlands.
