OL,6,FOliver says his family only found
OL,7,Fthese after Major Brock had died, he
OL,8,Fsays: "It was 20-something years after
OL,9,FGrandpa died, we were clearing the
OL,10,Fhouse and we found a secret drawer
OL,11,Funderneath a clock that contained a
OL,12,Ftin of tobacco, two pipes and a lot of
OL,13,Fdocuments relating to D-Day and the
OL,14,Factivities after."
