OL,4,Cunveiled for the first time
OL,6,FHe says: "That was the generation that
OL,7,Fclosed down these memories because the
OL,8,Fthings that I've now come to learn
OL,9,Fthat he saw and witnessed are horrific.
OL,11,F"They learned just to close down those
OL,12,Fmemories, so the idea that he would
OL,13,Fperhaps speak about it later in life,
OL,14,FI don't think I would have wanted to
OL,15,Fopen that for him."
OL,17,FMajor Brock is buried in the family
OL,18,Fplot at the Vale Church cemetery in
OL,19,FGuernsey.
